### Gallery

These example images have been generated using the
pepper's built-in reports.  The output type has been set to
[SVG](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SVG) in order to render both thumbnails
and high-resolution versions of each plot after wards. The latter can
be accessed by clicking on a thumbnail image.

The repository data is from the self-hosting repositories
of [Git](http://git.kernel.org/?p=git/git.git;a=summary) and
[Mercurial](http://selenic.com/repo/hg). The [MediaWiki Subversion
repository](http://svn.wikimedia.org/svnroot/mediawiki/)
has been used as an example of a large SVN repository
(>100000 revisions).  Additionally,a clone of [Linus Torvald's kernel
tree](http://git.kernel.org/?p=linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux-2.6.git;a=summary)
is presented.

